Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(184,183)\fs9\frz26\bord1.5}标题：（无题）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.71,0:02:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\pos(152,222)\fs9\frz25.5\1c000000\bord0}快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:07.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(348,67)\fs16\1c606060\bord0\b1}频道播放中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是让人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.94,0:03:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的脑袋就像西瓜落地一般被打得粉碎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.43,0:03:09.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.57,0:03:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是姐姐她…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我大约在一个月后出现在了她的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.23,0:03:27.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.85,0:03:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我挖掘她的畏罪心理
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:32.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,威胁她说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.98,0:03:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要使用我的力量就可以轻易地曝光她的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.80,0:03:39.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过她倒是比我想象中要来的固执
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:44.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我会永远缠着她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.94,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也能立刻就伤害到她最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.07,0:04:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一这么威胁  她马上就屈服了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和这孩子一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.35,0:04:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「Project Atum」原本是预定在2015年实施的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.79,0:04:21.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是就此放弃的话很可惜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.61,0:04:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,濑乃宫美纱希可是舍弃了人生的一切  全都押在这计划上了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.81,0:04:28.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君岛先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.97,0:04:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.20,0:04:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  濑乃宫妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:43.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的姐姐…  她现在还喜欢机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你在说些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.13,0:04:49.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她现在还喜欢机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.84,0:04:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁知道呢  不过她倒是没有舍弃游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.46,0:04:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直在玩一个名叫「Killballad」的游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.95,0:05:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.26,0:05:05.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样你就满足了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.12,0:05:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  因为对我来说机器人就是人之间的纽带
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.71,0:05:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人就是希望  是我和伙伴们努力的结晶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.09,0:05:17.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不给予机器人明确的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.67,0:05:19.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那它们连路都走不好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:22.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都是群需要照顾  让人无可奈何的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.43,0:05:26.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你只要好好面对它们  它们就会回应你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:32.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是Gun制造1号机还是2号机  就连种子岛机器3号改也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.84,0:05:34.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都如同我的孩子一般
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.75,0:05:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它们都是我最喜欢的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.77,0:05:40.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但姐姐却破坏了它们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她究竟是怎么想的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会感到悲伤吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:49.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是说无法感受到任何东西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.57,0:05:52.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.17,0:05:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.67,0:06:00.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  我绝不原谅让姐姐做出那种事的你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.02,0:06:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,君岛晃  我绝不原谅你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  放马过来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你能活下来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:13.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.45,0:06:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,邪恶的机器人要由正义的机器人来打倒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是约定俗成的老规矩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也许君岛先生你不知道  我就告诉你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨型直立行走机器人至今已经拯救了几十  数百次世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.63,0:06:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以这次机器人也会拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.18,0:06:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们所制造的机器人…  承载了我们梦想机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会击败你们的邪恶机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会打倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.24,0:06:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会打倒姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.08,0:06:49.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后拯救这个世界
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.36,0:06:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,300人委员会  「Project Atum」还有君岛晃全都是垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐什么的见鬼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么能输给完美无缺的姐姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.15,0:07:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无论多少次我都要说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.77,0:07:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义一定会胜利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取得胜利  再由我救出姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起  真是了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:18.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感动
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是你这么说了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:27.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要对这孩子见死不救  还要去杀死最爱的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.95,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这意味着什么  你就好好看清楚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.54,0:07:35.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手  住手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.76,0:07:38.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波霸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波霸个头啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:46.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干得好  太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.75,0:08:00.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个男人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.41,0:08:04.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.66,0:08:14.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正义的…巨型机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.72,0:08:17.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:18.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:23.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高同学
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.02,0:08:24.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大德学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.62,0:08:26.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.85,0:08:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  我总觉得有点坐立不安…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.99,0:08:33.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.13,0:08:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看了小亚希说话的那个视频了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.62,0:08:40.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.29,0:08:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说的巨型机器人一定是指这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  日高同学…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.22,0:08:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.58,0:08:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到今天  我都没有好好地跟你道过一次歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.38,0:08:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.93,0:09:02.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是这么想的话就帮我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.92,0:09:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日高同学
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.31,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你真的想道歉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.36,0:09:10.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不要说什么对不起  而用行动来表示吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让学姐谢罪  再强迫她当奴隶  而且是性奴隶…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.06,0:09:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么色情游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.84,0:09:26.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,古郡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.24,0:09:27.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样一来就全员到齐了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.51,0:09:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  果然你们都来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.23,0:09:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷  你为什么会来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  因为我一不小心看到了那个小鬼在乱叫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她肯定是打算干些什么吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.97,0:09:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.32,0:09:48.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  先让它能动起来吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.75,0:09:53.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(227,375,227,149)\fs16\frz-49.5\bord1.5}种子岛悬崖下发现身份不明的尸体  可能是谋杀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:55.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是真的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你指什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.57,0:10:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想脸色苍白恐怕就是指那种表情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:02.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我说了那是亚希和海…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.82,0:10:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不会说出去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.72,0:10:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也不会让你自首
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然我也不会去报警
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.96,0:10:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.67,0:10:29.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个时候我要是坦白了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:33.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说不定会责骂我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.86,0:10:48.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也真是个纠缠不清的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.73,0:11:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还不明白这些都是无用功吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是说了要让你做到最后吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:12.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希  海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.11,0:11:15.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你也真顽强
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.43,0:11:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般人明明一旦被我附身
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.17,0:11:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就会渐渐变成没有思想的牵线木偶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你居然想抵抗到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}亚希…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.59,0:11:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.62,0:11:34.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旧种子岛机场？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.78,0:11:36.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了  这样立刻就能去机库
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.33,0:11:39.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是说这种悠哉悠哉的话的时候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那机场已经很多年没用了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.81,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.80,0:11:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们好像联系不上新种子岛机场
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.05,0:11:51.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是被美纱姐他们镇压了吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.97,0:12:00.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看  种子岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.84,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总有种久别重逢的感觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:11.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,种子岛有这么小吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:18.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是感觉它有这么大吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:20.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定还真是这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.21,0:12:23.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:28.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座岛虽然很渺小  但却又很广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.61,0:12:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.09,0:12:38.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之这样电就算是通了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.18,0:12:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  有飞机吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:45.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是飞机也太近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.10,0:12:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.34,0:12:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快看那个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.10,0:12:54.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像在往这边飞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它不知道这机场已经被封锁了很多年了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.37,0:12:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.96,0:13:00.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  快看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.23,0:13:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搞什么飞机…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.32,0:13:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来是机体迫降啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.66,0:13:18.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它好像往这边过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  确实是往这边过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是不是该赶紧开溜？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.87,0:13:26.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.45,0:13:40.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上面究竟坐的是什么人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.94,0:13:43.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应当是时空跳跃过来的战士之类的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.71,0:13:45.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  必须是帅哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.21,0:13:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女孩子？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.43,0:13:56.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊  爱理炭！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.30,0:13:56.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.32,0:14:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.95,0:14:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有八汐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.29,0:14:04.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,部长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.93,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.37,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们为什么会在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:10.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎…这是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.65,0:14:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家看到我上传的视频了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:14.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小充你干了些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.13,0:14:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位天使是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.54,0:14:20.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  你们和她是初次见面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.63,0:14:22.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫行舟爱理
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.85,0:14:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  我跟着一起过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我就把刚才发生的情况如实说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:35.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我原本以为我的老婆只存在于二次元之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到她居然化身为三次元并从天而降了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.51,0:14:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然这样可能会被人吐槽说是轻小说看太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这才不是那样呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.93,0:14:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用管她
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.92,0:14:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,JAXA的工作人员及因太阳风暴的报道而无法回家的人们
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.83,0:14:55.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这所学校以及运动公园的体育馆内避难
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.10,0:15:00.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说…武装集团未能镇压机场和绑架芙劳子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.64,0:15:02.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而只占领了JAXA吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.11,0:15:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:05.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:10.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们依然因为太阳风暴抵达的假情报而慌乱着
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.03,0:15:13.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正中君岛晃的下怀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.72,0:15:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.50,0:15:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU说他已经到学校了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:16.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把爱理小姐送到保健室去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.74,0:15:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你身体没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.96,0:15:22.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是感激不尽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.37,0:15:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}三年二班
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.04,0:15:40.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\move(20,22,-7,22)\fs16\1c000000\bord0}Gun制造1号机改造方案
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.88,0:15:31.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…Gun制造1号机？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.54,0:15:35.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  总之我打算先把驱动器全换成磁单极子驱动器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:36.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来提高它的机动力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在此基础上  我还打算在手臂上安装打桩机
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:42.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打桩…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.39,0:15:43.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那种东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.10,0:15:45.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出于个人爱好做了个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.10,0:15:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后就摆出了这么一副得意洋洋的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我们有这么多时间来改造吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.17,0:15:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是做得做不到的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.60,0:15:54.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是只能放手去做
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.09,0:15:57.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是摇滚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.55,0:16:03.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  我们就来整理一下现在的情况吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:07.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,武装集团占领了宇宙中心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.91,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其目的是为了使用火箭将黑洞炸弹送上天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:15.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,预计他们将会在天气放晴后随时进行发射
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们必须在那之前改造好Gun制造1号机
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:21.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用其突破敌方的战斗力——SUMERAGI
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.07,0:16:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并阻止这一阴谋
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.19,0:16:28.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,火箭一旦成功发射  便会有五十亿人丧命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:29.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.32,0:16:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这责任也太重了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.80,0:16:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我们只能去做了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正是为此回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:37.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希穗…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.38,0:16:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占领了JAXA的是部长的姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.89,0:16:47.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后人质是你的爸爸对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.13,0:16:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家别把这事放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.70,0:16:56.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重点是「正义的机器人必胜」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:17:00.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为此  我们必须要齐心协力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.11,0:17:02.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.94,0:17:10.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  就由昴和DOKU来指挥大家
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.57,0:17:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们赶紧来改造Gun制造1号机吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淳就去帮昴的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:16.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:22.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芙劳子去看一下一个叫泽田的人刚刚传给海的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,泽田…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.54,0:17:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,网络信号还不太稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.41,0:17:27.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下载费了我好大一番功夫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.10,0:17:31.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过看起来是用来对付「SUMERAGI」的程序
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,IRUO.没法使用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.88,0:17:37.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快安装我事先委托开发的DG297
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这邮件怎么充满了高高在上的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.05,0:17:42.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这样正好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.11,0:17:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我一会传给你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.58,0:17:47.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出去有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.74,0:17:51.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海  你要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.91,0:17:54.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,电磁波发射装置
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:56.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它可以让人看到幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.23,0:17:58.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要用得好  不也可以成为武器吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.49,0:18:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这原本是君岛晃制造出来的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想调查一下的话应该会有所发现
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.44,0:18:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.72,0:18:08.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后这个男人也是一脸臭屁的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.58,0:18:10.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你们！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.39,0:18:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,究竟在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.72,0:18:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该说过机器人研究部已经解散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.20,0:18:19.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.56,0:18:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么能这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.55,0:18:22.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.72,0:18:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在可不是说这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要找借口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:26.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们无论如何也要干的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.82,0:18:28.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在这里签字吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.44,0:18:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您还是高抬贵手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经不是讨论学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:32.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,海…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.49,0:18:33.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是入部申请书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.27,0:18:34.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.22,0:18:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是让你们开工前先重建Robo部
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.36,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,万一出了什么事  学校就没法帮你们分担责任了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.99,0:18:46.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老师…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.10,0:18:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.25,0:18:50.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:53.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小充
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.42,0:18:54.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,教导主任
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.36,0:18:56.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些够了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.21,0:18:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:00.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好多！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.28,0:19:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是太少了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果算上主动申请要来帮你们的学生人数的话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.44,0:19:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.37,0:19:10.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  八汐～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.51,0:19:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来帮忙啦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  让你们久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.68,0:19:25.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.62,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把JAXA的技术人员给请来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.43,0:19:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.98,0:19:46.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爸爸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.63,0:19:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小亚希说的一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.56,0:19:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座岛虽然很渺小  但却又很广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.77,0:20:03.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.28,0:20:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,美纱希
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.46,0:20:16.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快跑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.42,0:20:18.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  只要这家伙还在我的体内
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.52,0:20:24.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.55,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.08,0:20:42.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我之前不是警告过你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:46.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抵抗过度的话  你可是会自我崩溃的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.65,0:20:48.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.68,0:20:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亚希和海他们一定会…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEZI姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.25,0:20:59.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我这就解放你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.46,0:21:01.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我无法理解
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.74,0:21:04.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快去那两人的身边…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.06,0:21:09.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,GEZI姐
